   The association Phonegate Alert
   Our main commitments:

   – to contribute to the use of mobile phones, digital tablets, connected
   objects or any other new technology to come using electromagnetic
   waves, under conditions that protect the health of users and in
   particular children and young people;

   – to participate in the identification, prevention and repair of damage
   caused to mobile victims on a physical, psychological and moral level,
   etc. and harm to their loved ones ;
